    "Although different structured and semi-structured approaches to find all related literature were carefully applied, the completeness of the selected literature cannot be fully assured.",
    "4 Nonetheless, the literature analyzed should provide a solid overview of the research domain and support the subsequent conclusions.",
    "After conducting the literature review, the papers were grouped according to the scientific methods and technologies used.",
    "In addition, the degree of understanding of the digital twin in the individual papers was analyzed.",
    "The result is a comprehensive overview of the entire research area of digital twins in seaports and terminals, which is visualized in Table 2."
